room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape The Room NYC in New York
review: We had our 10-year-old’s birthday party there and it was a blast. It was harder than I thought it would be but we liked it and I would recommend the Jurassic escape .

room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape The Room NYC in New York
review: It’s always great to come to Escape the room! We did the new Jurassic room, and it was the hardest room we have done....but still got out with 7 min!

room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape The Room NYC in New York
review: This was a fun experience. We we’re in 3 different rooms trying to reach our goal. There were lots of mental leaps you have to make but a good time was had by all, even the tweens with us. Would definitely recommend this room!
